description: Hi uwu holder, you are invited to our 1st uwuniversary party! Come celebrate the 1 year anniversary of uwucrew! Join us all day on September 5th for a day of games, movies, and fun!!! Be present in the Discord to claim your Slice of Cake uwu Quest Stamp. Thank you to everyone for all the support over the last year!
name: 1st uwuniversary Party Invitation!
